Face Mask Detection using Deep Learning (CNN + OpenCV) project structure. Here's what each file/folder is used for:

| File / Folder              | Purpose                                                                                                              |
| -------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **dataset/**               | Contains training images used to train the model. Usually has `with_mask` and `without_mask` folders.                |
| **face_detector/**         | Contains OpenCV face detection model files (Caffe/TensorFlow model) used to detect faces before mask classification. |
| **images/**                | Stores sample test images used for prediction and demonstration.                                                     |
| **Realtime_images/**       | Stores screenshots or images captured during real-time webcam detection.                                             |
| **.gitignore**             | Tells Git which files/folders should not be uploaded to GitHub.                                                      |
| **CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md**     | Project guidelines and rules for contributors.                                                                       |
| **detect_mask_image.py**   | Detects faces and predicts mask/no-mask from a single image.                                                         |
| **detect_mask_video.py**   | Detects masks in a video file frame-by-frame.                                                                        |
| **LICENSE**                | Legal permission document describing how others can use the project.                                                 |
| **mask_detector.model**    | Trained deep learning model used for mask classification. This is the final output after training.                   |
| **plot.png**               | Training graph showing Accuracy and Loss curves during model training.                                               |
| **README.md**              | Project documentation explaining installation, usage, dataset, and results.                                          |
| **requirements.txt**       | List of Python libraries required to run the project.                                                                |
| **search.py**              | Utility script, usually used for testing, searching, or image processing tasks.                                      |
| **train_mask_detector.py** | Main training script that trains the CNN model using the dataset and generates `mask_detector.model`.                |


